      "description": "Two-loop three-point top-quark loop family for $\\mathcal{O}(\\alpha \\alpha_s)$ $H \\to Z Z^*$ corrections. Six propagators carry $m_t$; one $(k_1-k_2)$ is massless gluon. Three off-shell legs with $p_1^2=m_Z^2$, $p_2^2=m_{Z^*}^2$, $(p_1+p_2)^2=m_H^2$ (4 scales). IBP with FIRE+LiteRed yields 41 masters in 9 top topologies. Canonical basis via maximal cuts; $\\varepsilon$-factorized DE has 4 square roots. Landen sub $u=-(1-x)^2/x$ rationalizes 3 of them; the remaining $r=\\sqrt{P(x,y,z)}$ with $P$ deg-8 defines a Calabi-Yau threefold in $\\mathbb{WP}^{1,1,1,1,4}$. Results as Chen iterated integrals over 31 dlog forms through $\\mathcal{O}(\\varepsilon^4)$.",
